11　　年　　8 　　月　　25　　日\r\n    　　　　　　　　　　　　　檢　察　官　王  聖  涵","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c3748%2c20221108%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,簡,3748,20221108,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"3748","JDATE":"20221108","JTITLE":"竊盜"}